
# Core language features #

X Type specialization. Figure out the type of generic expressions (such as if-expr) before runtime.
X Loops over collections
- Source reproduction. (currently this has many bugs)
X Infix-assignment operators, like +=
- Feedback (current support is very limited)
- Vector type
X Function overloading

# Cgame features #

Dataflow inspection / modification
 - Picking
 - Get a list of all the variables that influenced the position of something
 - UI element that displays the above list
 - Keybindings to toggle which values to modify
 - Mouse-dragging mode to send feedback to modifyable values

Save to source

Detect file modification

Keybindings for snapshotting

HUD UI elements
 - Display short status messages

Cairo integration for HUD
